ACARD TECHNOLOGY August Sales Fall 20.70% (Table) : 3126 TT

-- B y   J a n e t   O n g
-- 
2011-09-07T09:31:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/acard-technology-august-sales-fall-20-70-table-3126-tt.html
ACARD TECHNOLOGY said unconsolidated sales
in August fell 20.70% to NT$15,512,000 from NT$19,560,000,
according to a statement filed to the  Taiwan Stock Exchange .  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales             15,512           19,560    
YOY%             -20.70%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales            143,675          182,507    
YOY%             -21.28% 
=================================================================
 